      "title": "How to Never Lose Tic Tac Toe Again",
      "excerpt": "Tic Tac Toe is a solved game, thus it has a known optimal strategy.\nWith perfect play from both sides, the game ends in a draw.\nThat means you can memorize a compact set of practical rules and never lose!\n\nIn this blog I explain how I discovered it, and you'll find out how a perfect player thinks through an interactive and intuitive demo.",
